text: L'Haÿ-les-Roses is a commune. It is in the Val-de-Marne department in France. It is in the southern suburbs of Paris, from the center. 31,417 people lived here in 2018. The Roseraie du Val-de-Marne is here. == Related pages == * Communes of the Val-de-Marne department == References == Category:Communes in Val-de-Marne Category:Subprefectures in France
title: L'Haÿ-les-Roses
